data.title: Music Box Theater
data.meta_description: Since 2011 The Music Box Theater has provided a venue for people to enjoy popular music from across the decades, great sketch comedy and cabaret concerts in their custom- tailored state of the art performing facility. The Music Box believes that Houstonians deserve a consistent, dependable place to relax, have a drink or two, laugh and listen to great live music. Comprised of 5 professional Houston based actor/singers and their amazing 4 piece band.
data.text: Since 2011 The Music Box Theater has provided a venue for people to enjoy popular music from across the decades, great sketch comedy and cabaret concerts in their custom- tailored state of the art performing facility. The Music Box believes that Houstonians deserve a consistent, dependable place to relax, have a drink or two, laugh and listen to great live music. Comprised of 5 professional Houston based actor/singers and their amazing 4 piece band, The Music Box writes and produces seven 2 act comedies per year, centered around varying musical themes.
